Yesu Kristo, Owíe Dawid mʋ na, Abraham mʋ na ámʋ ɩlɩ́ntɔ nɩ́.
Bɛbláa mʋ bɛɛ “Betlehem wúluá ɩbʋ Yudea ɔmátɔ́. Alɩ́ Bulu ɔnɔ́sʋ́ ɔtɔɩ́pʋ́ ɔkʋ lɔ́wanlɩ́n tswɩ nɩ.
‘Mlɩla anɩ Wíe ɔkpa.
Mʋ́ ɔma a, Yesu lónu ánɩ́ bakɩ́tá Yohane tswɩ obu, oleyinkí ba Galilea ɔsʋlʋ́sʋ.
tsúfɛ́ obówun amʋ́ nwɛ.
Támɛ mɩ́ mʋ́ ndɛ mlɩ bláa mbɛ́ɛ, máka tɔtɔɔtɔ kʋ́ráá. Mápʋ ɔsʋ́sʋ́ ká ntam, tsúfɛ́ Bulu owíe obíá igyi.
Mákpa anɩ wá ɩsɔ́kɩtɔ, mboún lɛ anɩ tsu Ɔbʋnsám ɩbɩtɔ.’
Ma bʋ́ʋ mlɩtɔá mʋ bi ɔkʋ́lɩ́ mʋ bodobodo a, obótsu ibwi wá mʋ ɩbɩtɔ?
Támɛ bɛ́lɛ Israelfɔ ámʋ́ʋ́ tɛkɩ bʋgyi Bulu iwíegyí ámʋtɔ atsiápʋ́ amʋ lɛ́ ɩnʋ, tswɩ amʋ́ wá oklúntɔ. Ɩnʋ́ isú mʋ́a kpisíi bʋ nɩ.”
Ɩnʋ ɔlɔkʋsʋ́ nátɩ́ yɔ́ wóyítɔ́.
Yesu léki awúlu pʋ́ nkuda fɛ́ɛ́ asɩ, súná atɔ́ Yudafɔ ofíakpa. Ɔlɛda Bulu iwíegyí ámʋ ɩwɩ asʋn wankláán ɔkan. Ɔlɛtsa ɩlɔ kugyíkʋ fɛ́ɛ́.
Mlɩmánya nyankpʋsa ifú. Ɔbɛ́talɩ́ mɔ́ mlɩ ɔyʋlʋ́ʋ, támɛ ɔmɛ́ɛtalɩ́ mɔ́ mlɩ ɔkláa. Mboún ɔhá ánɩ́ mlɩnyá ifú gyí Bulu. Mʋ ɔbɛ́talɩ́ yíntá ɔyʋlʋ́ʋ mʋ́a ɔkláa amʋ fɛ́ɛ́ ɩsʋbɩtɩ́ ogyá ánɩ́ ɩtamaduntɔ.
blɩ́ bɛɛ, ‘Anɩlapléí ansigyísʋ́, mlɩmɛ́tsa. Mʋ́ sʋ anɩlalá wá awɩrɛhɔ ɩlʋ, támɛ mlɩmósu.’
Mʋ́ʋ́ ɔlɛda amʋ́ ɔlá ɔbɛ́ɛ, bʋmáha ahá abʋbɩ mʋ.
Tsúfɛ́ ɔha asʋn blɩ́hɛ́ Bulu ɔbɔ́pʋhá mʋ asʋ ntɛ́ɛ ɩpɔ́n.
Bɛ́kɩ lákɩ, támɛ bʋmóowun mʋ́.
Mʋ́ʋ́ Yesu lɛ́lɛ mʋ́ ɔnɔ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mɩ́, Nyankpʋsa-Mʋ-Bi ánfɩ gyí atɔ́-abí wankláán odupʋ́ ámʋ nɩ.
Otsibi amʋ mʋ yin lɛ́ha mʋ ɔlɛbláa Herode ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ndekléá fʋpʋ́ Asú Ɔbɔpʋ́ Yohane nwun dɩnka ɩlɩ́nsʋ́ ha mɩ sésééséi.”
“Ntogyi sʋ́ fʋ́ akasɩ́pʋ́ amʋ bʋtamagyi anɩ anáin amándɩ́ɛ́sʋ́. Bʋtamafwɩ́ ɩbɩ amándɩ́ɛ́ ɔkpasʋ asa bʋtegyi atɔ́?”
Ahá ámʋ ɔnɔ́ lobwie amʋ́ brɛ́á bowun amúmu bʋdɛtɔɩ́, abubúpʋ ɩwɩ lawá amʋ́ ɔnlɩn, abɔ bʋna, ansibi abwiepʋ́ ɛ́ bʋdɛ atɔ́ wúun, bɛkanfʋ́ Israel Bulu ámʋ.
Ɩnʋ ɔlɛda amʋ́ ɔlá kpákpáákpá ɔbɛ́ɛ, bʋmábláa ɔhaa ánɩ́ mʋgyí Kristo amʋ.
Asʋ́n ánfɩ lɛhɩɛ han akasɩ́pʋ́ amʋ.
Támɛ osúmpʋ́ amʋ má tɔtɔá ɔbɔ́pʋká ɩkɔ ámʋ sʋ á, owíe amʋ lɛ́ha ɔbɛ́ɛ bʋfɛ́ɛ mʋa mʋ ka, mʋ abí pʋ́ mʋ atɔ́ fɛ́ɛ́ pʋ́kɩ́tá ɩkɔ ámʋtɔ.
Bu fʋ́ sɩ́ mʋa fʋ́ yín, afʋdwɛ fʋ́ bá fɛ́ fʋ́ ɩwɩ.”
Bɔ́pʋ mɩ́ wá ahá ánɩ́ bʋmegyí Yudafɔ ɩbɩtɔ bɔ́bwɛ mɩ́ ahinlá, bɔ́nwɛn mɩ́ mplɩ, dá mɩ́ mántá oyikpalíhɛsʋ. Támɛ Bulu ɔbɛ́lakʋ́sʋ́a mɩ ɛkɛ sáásɩ́ tsú afúlitɔ.”
Ɔdɔm amʋ́ʋ́ bʋbuo mʋ amʋ bɛlɛ mʋ́ ɔnɔ́ bɛɛ, “Ɔ́nɩ gyí Yesu, Bulu ɔnɔ́sʋ́ ɔtɔɩ́pʋ́ amʋ́ʋ́ otsú Nasaret wúluá ɩbʋ Galilea ɔmátɔ́ ámʋ nɩ.”
Ndɔ mʋ wie amʋ lɛ́trá wa mʋ asúmpʋ́ bámbá ánɩ́ bʋtsɔ dʋn agyankpapʋ amʋ. Apafɔ ámʋ bɔbwɛ amʋ́ ɛ́ alɩ kɛ́n.
Mʋ́ sʋ anɩdɛ́ fʋ́ fɩtɛ́ anu. Anɩ mbla lɛ́ha ɔkpa ánɩ́ akáa lampóo ha Roma owíe dɛhɛn Kaesare, ntɛ́ɛ anɩmáka?”
‘Anɩ Wíe Bulu lɛ́bláa mɩ́ Wíe ɔbɛ́ɛ,
“Mlɩ Farisifɔ pʋ́ Mose mbla asunápʋ́, apinabwɛbí abwɛpʋ́, mlɩgyɔwɩ nɩ́. Mlɩlabwɛ́ fɛ́ ntsán ánɩ́ bakpá mʋ́ afá futútúútú, mʋ́ ɩwɩ lawá akɩ́lɛ. Támɛ mʋ́tɔ́ mʋ́ á, afúli awú pʋ́ atɔ plɔ́hɛ́ sɔ́ɔ́n bɔ́ mʋ́.
Amenyapʋ́ pʋ́ abí-ayín ánɩ́ bʋpia abi bɔbwɛ alɩ brɛ́ ámʋtɔ, bʋgyɔ́wɩ nɩ́.
Ɩ́nɩ sʋ olefi asɩ ɔdɛ mʋ aba asúmpʋ́ da, mʋa ntá abʋpʋ́ bʋdɛ atɔ́ gyí si amʋ́, bʋdɛ ntá núu bʋ á,
Mʋ́ʋ́ oyin ámʋ lɛ́bláa mʋ asúmpʋ́ amʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, ‘Mlɩswɩɩ mʋ sika pɛpɛ kɛntɛ kʋlɛ amʋ ha ɔmʋamʋ́ʋ́ alanyá akɛntɛ idú ámʋ.
Ɔnɔkwalɩ ndɛ mlɩ bláa. Ɔyɩ́tɔ́ ɔtɩ́nɛgyíɔtɩ́nɛ́á bɛ́da Bulu asʋn wankláán ámʋ ɔkan a, bɛ́blɩ́ tɔ́ ánfɩ ɔtsɩ ánfɩ labwɛ́ ánfɩ pʋ́káɩ́n mʋsʋ.”
Ɔlɛtrá yinkí ba bowun ánɩ́ akasɩ́pʋ́ amʋ bʋtráa bʋdɛdɩdɩ, tsúfɛ́ dɩdɩ́ dɛ amʋ́ bʋ.
Támɛ Petro lɔ́wa ɔnɔlɩ́ ahá ámʋ fɛ́ɛ́ ansɩ́tɔ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mmeyín asʋ́n ánfɩ fʋdɛblɩ́ ánfɩ ɩwɩ kʋkʋʋkʋ.”
Mʋ́ʋ́ Pilato lɛ́trá fɩtɛ́ amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ntɔ mbwɛ́ɛ Yesu, bʋtɛtɩ́ mʋ Kristo, (ɔhá ámʋ́ʋ́ Bulu ladá mʋ ofúli amʋ)?”
Yesu lɛ́trá kplʋ́n kʋ́klʋ́kʋ́ʋ́, ɔlɛlɛ ɔŋɛ́.
Mʋ́ sʋ ntsán agyópʋ amʋ botsulá hɔ kɔ́ba amʋ, begyi dɩnká Bulu igyí ahapʋ́ dɛhɛn amʋ asʋn blɩ́hɛ́ anfɩsʋ. Ɔnɔ́ ánfɩ bɛha amʋ́ ánfɩ lobwie wá Yudafɔ ɔmá ámʋ fɛ́ɛ́tɔ́ bɔfʋn ndɛ.
Yesu mʋa mʋ akasɩ́pʋ́ bɔyɔ Kapernaum wúlutɔ. Ɔlɔyɔ Yudafɔ ofíakpa yósuná atɔ́ ɔkpʋ́nʋ́ ɔdakɛ́.
“Ntɔ asʋ́n oyin ánfɩ dɛ́blɩ́ alɩ? Megyí mbusuo álabɔ́ á? Ma ɛ́ ɔbɛ́talɩ́ sí lakpan kíé ahá dʋn Bulu nkʋlɛ?”
Ahá ámʋ bɔdʋbɩ. Mʋ́ sʋ ɔlɛbláa mʋ akasɩ́pʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, bʋdúnka ɔklʋn kʋ yaɩ ha mʋ, mɛ́nɩ bʋmóoputá mʋ.
Ɩkʋ ɛ́ lɔwʋlɩ́ abʋtásʋ́, ɔtɩ́nɛ́á ɩsɩ kpalobí dɩn. Ɩlɔwa ɔsa kwɛ,
Ɩnʋ Yesu lɛ́fɩtɛ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ntɔ Bulu iwíegyí ámʋ lɛlɩan? Ntɛ́ɛ yébi mɔmʋ nɔ́pʋsúná alɩá igyi?
Brɛ́á olowie ɔklʋn amʋtɔ á, oyin ámʋ́ʋ́ tɛkɩ ɔŋɛ laláhɛ tsie mʋtɔ ámʋ lókokóli mʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, ɔhá amʋbuo mʋ natɩ.
Ɩ́nɩá bʋmɔhɔ mʋ gyi sʋ ɔmɛtalɩ́ bwɛ́ ofúla kʋkʋ, dʋn ahá kpalobí akʋsʋ ɔ́lɔpʋ ɩbɩ dɩ́nká, tsá amʋ́ ɩlɔ.
Támɛ ahá tsɔtsɔɔtsɔ bowun amʋ́, bɩ́ ɔtɩ́nɛ́á bɔyɔ́. Mʋ́ sʋ botsu awúlu ámʋ fɛ́ɛ́sʋ́, tsíí ɔsrɩ́ɩ gyankpá yówie ɔtɩ́nɛ́ ámʋ́ʋ́ Yesu aná bɔyɔ́ ámʋ.
Alɩ kɛ́n nɩ́ bʋmɔkʋ́gyʋ́ra ɩwɩ á, bʋtamagyi tɔ́á bɔpʋtsúa bíásʋ́ ba nɩ. Amándɩ́ɛ́ bámbá kʋ aná ɛ́ bʋ ɩnʋ, bʋtráa bʋdɛ mʋ́tɔ́ tsú nwɛ núu ntsu, nlɔ́ pʋ́ nlanka ɩwɩ.)
Yesu lɛ́natɩ́ Tiro ɩnʋ yɔ́ Sidon yóbomlí kplɩ́ ba Dekapoli  awúlu amʋ nsáɩntɔ asa ɔlɛladʋ́ yɔ́ Galilea ɔpʋ ɔnɔ́.
Ɩnʋ Yesu lɛ́fɩtɛ́ amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ɩmɔkʋ́wánkɩ́ mlɩ kɩ?”
Ɔlɛlɛ mʋ́ ɔnɔ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ɔnɔkwalɩ igyi, ánɩ́ Elia obégyankpá bá bɛla tógyítɔ́ yáɩ́ wankláán. Mʋ́ ntogyi sʋ́ Bulu asʋn wanlɩ́nhɛ́ amʋ kɛ́n lɛ́blɩ́ tsú mɩ́ ɩwɩ ɔbɛ́ɛ, mɩ́, Nyankpʋsa-Mʋ-Bi ánfɩ nɛ́hɩɛ wun ipian, ahá bɔ́sʋpáa mɩ?
Tsúfɛ́ ɔhá ánɩ́ ɔmɔkʋsʋ́ lɩ́ɩ́ anɩsʋ buo anɩ.
Yesu lɛ́kɩ mʋ díín, mʋ asʋ́n lɔwa mʋ ɔdwɛ. Mʋ́ʋ́ ɔlɛbláa mʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ɩlasí tokukʋlɛá fɔ́bwɛ. Yɛfɛ fʋ́ ɩwɩsʋ atɔ́ fɛ́ɛ́, afʋye kɔ́ba amʋ ha ahiánfɔ, mɛ́nɩ fénya siadɩɛ ɔsʋ́sʋ́. Fɔbwɛ́ mʋ́ tá á, ba afʋbobuo mɩ.”
Bokpolí ansibi obwiepʋ́ ámʋ, bɛbláa mʋ bɛɛ, “Fʋ́ klʋn ɩdɩ́ fʋ́ asɩ, afʋkʋsʋ ba. Ɔdɛ fʋ́ tɩ!”
Ɩ́nɩ sʋ ndɛ mlɩ bláa mbɛ́ɛ, tógyítɔ́á mlɔkʋ́lɩ́ Bulu á, mlɩhogyi ánɩ́ mlɩlanyá mʋ́ dodo. Mlɩ ɩbɩ bɛ́da mʋ́.
Mʋ́ʋ́ ɔlɛbláa amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mʋ́mʋ́ mlɩpʋ tɔ́á igyi Kaesare klɛ́ ha Kaesare, amlɩpʋ mʋ́á igyi Bulu klɛ́ ɛ́ ha Bulu.”
Yesu létsiá mantáa tswɩtswɩ dáka Bulu ɔtswɛ́kpa ɩnʋ, ɔdɛ ahá kɩ́ɩ bʋdɛpʋ amʋ́ tswɩtswɩ bɔwa mʋ́tɔ́. Ahá ánɩ́ amʋ́ ɩbɩtɔ bʋ odwin bʋdɛpʋ kɔ́ba akpɔnkpɔntɩ bɔwa.
Ɩnʋ Bulu ɔbɔ́wa mʋ abɔpʋ bɛ́yɛkpa mʋ ahá ámʋ́ʋ́ alalɛ́ ámʋ tsú ɔyɩ́ afʋnka ana ámʋ fɛ́ɛ́sʋ́.
Yesu lɛ́bláa amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mlɩ ahá dúanyɔ ánfɩtɔ ɔkʋlɛá mɩ́a mʋnyɔ ɩbɩ da ɔlɛpɛtɔ ɔbɛ́lɛ mɩ́ há nɩ́.
Ntsie mlɩ wá Bulu ɔtswɛ́kpa wunsɩnɛ́sʋ́ ɩnʋ ekekegyíɛkɛ, ndɛ mlɩ atɔ́ suná, mlɩmɛ́kɩtá mɩ́ ɛkɛkɛɛkɛ. Ɩ́nɩ lahá Bulu asʋn wanlɩ́nhɛ́ amʋ ɩlaba mʋ́tɔ́.”
Mʋ́ sʋ Pilato lɛ́fɩtɛ́ Yesu ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Kɩ asʋ́n tsɔtsɔɔtsɔá baká dɩ́nká fʋ́sʋ́, fʋma mʋ́ ɔnɔ́ lɛ́?”
Brɛ́á dódúanyɔ lɛda á, owí lɛta ɔsʋlʋ́ʋ amʋsʋ fɛ́ɛ́ alɩɩ yɔ́fʋn ntʋ́pwɛ dɔsatɔ.
Ɔha ánɩ́ olohogyi, bɔbɔ mʋ asú á, Bulu ɔbɔ́hɔ mʋ nkpa, támɛ ɔhá ánɩ́ omohogyi obégyi pɔ́n.
Elisabet lɛ́blɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ɩ́nɩ mɩ́ Wíe Bulu labwɛ́ há mɩ́ nɩ́. Alawun mɩ́ nwɛ, dɩ́nkɩ́ nsʋ́pa lɛ́ mɩ́sʋ́ ahátɔ.”
Alapʋ́ mʋ túmi bwɛ́ atɔ́ akpɔnkpɔntɩ,
pʋ́ ahá ánɩ́ bʋtamafia anɩ ɩbɩtɔ.
Ɔtsáwʋlɛ pɛ́ á, Bulu-abɔpʋ tsɔtsɔɔtsɔ bɛba bɛtsɩá Bulu-ɔbɔpʋ amʋtɔ, bʋdɛ Bulu kanfʋ́ bɛɛ,
Kebi ámʋ lɛ́dan, nyá ɔwʋnlɩ́n, nyá nyánsa, Bulu ɛ́ lóyulá mʋ.
Yohane lɛ́bláa amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mlɩmátswɩ dɩnká ahá. Mlɩhɔ tɔ́á bɛɛ mlɩhɔ́ɔ.”
Yesu lɛ́lɛ mʋ́ ɔnɔ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Bɔwanlɩ́n wá Bulu asʋ́n ámʋtɔ bɛɛ, ‘Megyí atogyihɛ wʋlɛ nyankpʋsa ogyíi tsia nkpa.’ ”
Ɔblɔ́ lɛhɩɛ kɩ́tá ahá ámʋ́ʋ́ bʋbʋ ofíakpa ɩnʋ ámʋ, brɛ́á bonu Yesu asʋn blɩ́hɛ́ anfɩ.
Ɛkɛ ɔkʋ Yesu bʋ wúlu kʋsʋ, ɩlɔ pɛpɛ ɔlɔpʋ́ ɔkʋ lówun mʋ. Ɩnʋ ɔlɛbɛda akpawunu, pʋ́ ɔsʋkpɩ yi ɔsʋlʋ́tɔ, kókóli mʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Owíé, nɩ́ fótsulá á, fɛ́talɩ́ há mɩ́ ɩwɩ bɛ́plɩ.”
Yesu lɛ́fɩtɛ́ amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mlɩmɔ́kʋ́kla nu tɔ́á Owíe Dawid lɔ́bwɛ brɛ́á akʋ́n dɛ mʋa mʋ abúopʋ kɩ?
Mlɩ ánɩ́ mlɩdɛ́mɔsɩ́ séi, mlɩgyɔwɩ nɩ́.
Tsúfɛ́ ɔtɔdwɛ́ anɩ pɩ. Mʋléyi anɩ ofíakpa kʋ́ráá há anɩ nɩ́.”
Támɛ ɔhá ánɩ́ ɔbʋ Bulu nyánsa á, mʋ tsíátɔ́ tɛlɛ́ mʋ́ ɔwan.”
Abí ámʋ́ʋ́ ɩlɔwʋlɩ́ abʋtásʋ́ amʋ gyí ahá ámʋ́ʋ́ bonú asʋ́n ámʋ pɛ́, bahɔ mʋ́ ansigyísʋ́, támɛ bʋma nlín. Mʋ́ sʋ bʋtamahogyi wa ɔpá. Nɩ́ ɩsɔ́kɩ kʋ inyá tʋ́ amʋ́ pɛ́, badɩda.
Mʋ́ sʋ oyin ámʋ léki wúlu amʋ fɛ́ɛ́ fíá, ɔdɛ toyilé ámʋ́ʋ́ Yesu labwɛ́ há mʋ amʋ blɩ́ wúlu amʋtɔ fɛ́ɛ́.
Brɛ́á ɔdɔm amʋ bɛbɩ ánɩ́ ɔbʋ ɩnʋ á, begya mʋ ɔkpa yɔ́ ɩnʋ. Yesu lɔ́hɔ amʋ́ atúu, ɔlɛbláa amʋ́ Bulu iwíegyí amʋ ɩwɩ asʋ́n, ɔlɛtsa amʋ́á bʋdɛlɔ.
Nobobwií ɩpa há fʋ́ akasɩ́pʋ́ amʋ mbɛ́ɛ, bʋgyáa mʋ́ lɛ mʋtɔ, támɛ bʋmɛtalɩ́.”
Nɩ́ mlowíé wóyígyíwóyítɔ́á a, mlɩgyankpa bla amʋ́ mlɩaa, ‘Bulu ɔhá mlɩ iwilwii.’
Mʋ́ ɔyɩ kɛhɛ a, Samariayin amʋ lɛ́lɛ sika futútú anyɔ há afɔɔ́ ɔswɩɩ́kpá ɩnʋsʋ ɔkɩ́pʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, ‘Kɩ mʋsʋ ha mɩ. Nɩ́ feyintá tɔkʋ tsɩ́a a, neyínkí nɛ́ka fʋ́.’ ”
Nɩ́ Satan iwíe ogyíkpá labɔ́ɩ́ anyɔ, bʋdɛ aba kɔ á, mʋ iwíegyí bɛ́dɩda. Támɛ mlɩdɛ́blɩ́ mlɩaa, Beelsebul dátɔ́ ndɛ ɔŋɛ laláhɛ gyáa lɛ ahátɔ.
Ɩ́nɩ désuná ánɩ́ mlɩlatsúlá dɩ́nká mlɩ anáin bwɛhɛ́ ámʋsʋ nɩ́. Tsúfɛ́ mlɩ anáin bɔmɔ amʋ́, mlɩ ɛ́ mlɩlapwɛ́ amʋ́ ntsán.
Mlɩkɩ aklankpa. Bʋtamadú, bʋtamasɩ́ɛ́tɩ́ wá ɩdantɔ. Bʋma ɩdan ntɛ́ɛ ɩfa, támɛ Bulu tɛhá amʋ́ atogyihɛ. Mlɩmá labi dʋn mbubwi?
Yesu lɛ́trá bláa ahá ámʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Nɩ́ nyankpʋ obílá bʋsʋ á, mlɩtɛblɩ́ mlɩaa, ndɛ nyankpʋ obótswie, lɛ́lɛ́ ototswie.
“Mlɩbɔ mbɔ́dɩ́ amlɩtsʋn obu-ɔnɔ́ kplánhɛ amʋtɔ. Tsúfɛ́ ahá tsɔtsɔɔtsɔ bɔ́bɔ mbɔ́dɩ́ ánɩ́ bɔ́tsʋn wie ɩnʋ, támɛ bʋmɛ́ɛtalɩ́.
Onyɔɔsɩ ɛ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, ‘Nahɔ nnantswie yínhɛ́ idú, bópulipúli mɩ́ ndɔtɔ há mɩ́. Nɛyɛ́kapʋ́ amʋ́ kɩ. Mʋ́ sʋ mlɩkɩta mʋ́tɔ́ ha mɩ.’
Brɛ́á oleyintá atɔ́ ámʋ tá á, akʋ́n kpɔnkpɔntɩ kʋ lɛ́ba ɔmá ámʋtɔ, ɔlɔwa akʋ́n dɩ bɩ.
Mʋ́ sʋ nɩ́ mlɩmá ɔnɔkwalɩ ɔyɩ́tɔ́ atɔ́sʋ́ a, ma mɛɛ ɔbɔ́hɔ mlɩsʋ gyi, pʋ́ ɔsʋ́sʋ́ atɔ́ onutó wá mlɩ ɩbɩtɔ?
Ɔtɛdá osúmpʋ́ amʋ ɩpán ɔbɛ́ɛ, alabwɛ́ tɔ́á mɔwa mʋ bwɛ? Ɛkɛkɛɛkɛ!
Ɩnʋ Yesu lɛ́ha yébi kʋ pʋ́súná ánɩ́ bʋbɔ́ɔ mpáɩ brégyíbrɛ́, ɩmákpɔn amʋ́.
Yesu lɛ́tɩ akasɩ́pʋ́ dúanyɔ ámʋ ya ɩtsɛ́tɔ́, ɔlɛbláa amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ayɔ́ Yerusalem. Ɩnʋ́ asʋ́n ámʋ́ʋ́ Bulu ɔnɔ́sʋ́ atɔɩ́pʋ́ amʋ bɔwanlɩ́n tsú mɩ́, Nyankpʋsa-Mʋ-Bi ánfɩ ɩwɩ ámʋ fɛ́ɛ́ bɛ́ba mʋ́tɔ́ nɩ́.
Mʋ́ʋ́ ɔlɛbláa osúmpʋ́ amʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, ‘Fabwɛ́ atɔ́. Osúmpʋ́ wankláán fʋ́gyi. Ɩ́nɩá fawá ɔnɔkwalɩ ɩtɔ́ túkúrííbi ánfɩ ɩwɩ sʋ á, nɔ́pʋ awúlu idú wá fʋ́ ɩbɩtɔ, fɛ́kɩ mʋ́sʋ́.’
Oletsiá súná atɔ́ Bulu ɔtswɛ́kpa ɩnʋ ekekegyíɛkɛ. Bulu igyí ahapʋ́ dɛhɛn, Mose mbla asunápʋ́ pʋ́ Yudafɔ ahandɛ amʋ bodunká ɔkpa ánɩ́ bɔ́tsʋn mʋ́sʋ́ mɔ́ mʋ.
Bɛlɛ mʋ́ ɔnɔ́ bɛɛ, “Kaesare.”
Yesu akasɩ́pʋ́ akʋ bʋdɛtɔɩ́ tsú alɩá bɔpʋ abwi ánɩ́ ɩbʋ bíá yi Bulu ɔtswɛ́kpa amʋ, pʋ́ atokiehɛ́ wankláán lá mʋ́tɔ́. Támɛ Yesu lɛ́bláa amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ,
Tsúfɛ́ ɩbɛ́ba ɔyɩ́tɔ́ ahá fɛ́ɛ́sʋ́.
Ma dʋ́n mʋ ba? Ɔhá ánɩ́ otsie ɔpʋ́nʋ́asɩ lóó, ntɛ́ɛ ɔhá ánɩ́ odesúm ɔpʋ́nʋ́ ámʋ asɩ? Megyí ɔhá ámʋ́ʋ́ otsie mʋ́ asɩ ámʋ dʋn? Támɛ mbʋ mlɩtɔ fɛ́ osúmpʋ́.
Támɛ brɛ́á bosun agyabi wunsɩnɛ́sʋ́ ɩnʋ, bʋtsie mʋ́ asɩ á, Petro léyétsiá amʋ́ wá.
Mʋ́ sʋ ɔlɛfɩtɛ́ Yesu asʋ́n tsɔtsɔɔtsɔ, támɛ Yesu mɛ́lɛ kʋkʋ ɔnɔ́.
Támɛ onyɔɔsɩ amʋ lɔ́wa ɩyɩn wá mʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Fʋmɛdɛ́ Bulu ifú nya! Fʋ́a mʋnyɔ fɛ́ɛ́ dɛ́ ɩsʋbɩtɩ́ kʋlɛ hɔ́ɔ.
Bulu létin amʋ́ ansɩ́. Mʋ́ sʋ bʋmɛbɩ mʋ.
Ɩnʋ olobwií amʋ́ agywɩɩn, mɛ́nɩ bónu Bulu asʋn wanlɩ́nhɛ́ amʋ asɩ.
Bɛtrá fɩtɛ́ mʋ bɛɛ, “Fʋ́gyí Bulu ɔnɔ́sʋ́ ɔtɔɩ́pʋ́ amʋ́ʋ́ ɔbɛ́ba amʋ?”
Filipo lɛ́bláa mʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ba afʋbɛkɩ.”
Támɛ Yesu mɔ́pʋ ansɩ́ dɩ́nká amʋ́sʋ́, tsúfɛ́ oyin alɩá amʋ́ fɛ́ɛ́ bʋgyi.
Ɩnʋ ɔlɛha amʋ́ yébi ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ɔká otsiápʋ bʋ́ mʋ ka. Ɔká otsiápʋ amʋ mʋ nyawie ɛ́ tetsíá ɔká otsiákpá ɩnʋ, mɛ́nɩ ansɩ́ bégyi mʋ nɩ́ onú mʋ nyawie amʋ ɔmɛ. Alɩ kɛ́n ansɩ́ dɛ mɩ́ gyí séi nɩ́.
Mlɩ Samariafɔ mlɩméyín ɔhá ánɩ́ mlɩdésum. Anɩ Yudafɔ mʋ́ anɩyin ɔhá ánɩ́ anɩdésum, tsúfɛ́ Yudafɔsʋ ɩna nkpahɔ́ɔ lɛba ɔyɩ́tɔ́.
Brɛ́á ɔyɔ́ á, mʋ asúmpʋ́ bɛba befia mʋ, bláa mʋ bɛɛ, “Fʋ́ bí ámʋ lanyá nkpa.”
Alahá mɩ́ túmi ɔbɛ́ɛ, ngyíi ahá asʋ́n, tsúfɛ́ mɩ́gyí Nyankpʋsa-Mʋ-Bi ámʋ nɩ.
Yesu lɛ́bláa mʋ akasɩ́pʋ́ amʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mlɩha amʋ́ abʋtsiatsia asɩ.” Ahá ámʋ fɛ́ɛ́ betsiá ɩfásʋ́. Ayin ánɩ́ bʋbʋ amʋ́tɔ́ bɔ́bwɛ fɛ́ mpɩ́m-nu (5,000).
Tɔ́á mɩ́ Sɩ́ ámʋ tekle gyí, ɔhagyíɔha ánɩ́ olowun mɩ́, mʋ Bi ánfɩ, hɔ mɩ gyi obénya nkpa ánɩ́ ɩtamatá. Nɔ́kʋsʋ́a mʋ tsú afúlitɔ ɛkɛ tráhɛ amʋ.”
(Simon Iskariot mʋ bi Yuda ɔdɛ á. Tsúfɛ́ ogyi akasɩ́pʋ́ dúanyɔ ámʋtɔ ɔkʋlɛ. Mʋ ɔbɛ́lɛ mʋ há nɩ́.)
Ɩnʋ bekle abʋkɩta mʋ, támɛ bʋmɔpʋ ɩbɩ da mʋ, tsúfɛ́ mʋ brɛ́ mɔkʋ́fʋn.
Brɛ́á bʋtráa bʋdɛ asʋ́n ámʋ fɩtɛ́ plá á, olobwií tsíá, bláa amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mlɩtɔ ɔhá ánɩ́ ɔmɔkʋ́bwɛ́ lakpan kɩ ogyánkpa da ɔtsɩ ánfɩ ibwi.”
Ɔkpábi tamatsíá mʋ wie wóyí yɔ́, obí tetsíá mʋ sɩ wóyí yɔ́.
Ɩlasí kpalobí owí ɔbɛ́ta. Ɔhaa mɛ́ɛtalɩ́ trá yɔ agyʋ́má. Mʋ́ sʋ ilehián ánɩ́ abɔ́yɔ agyʋ́má ámʋ́ʋ́ ɔhá ámʋ́ʋ́ ɔlɔwa mɩ́ sɩ́sɩ́ ámʋ lɔ́wa mɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ nyɔ́ɔ amʋ.
Anɩ fɛ́ɛ́ anɩyin ánɩ́ Bulu tamanú lakpan abwɛpʋ́ isu. Ɔhá ánɩ́ otobú mʋ́, otegyi mʋ mblasʋ isu otonú.
Amʋ́tɔ́ akʋ bɛblɩ́ bɛɛ, “Ɔŋɛ laláhɛ bʋ mʋtɔ. Mʋ nwun ideyintá. Ɔhaa mátrá nu mʋ asʋn blɩ́hɛ́.”
Mʋ akasɩ́pʋ́ amʋ bɛfɩtɛ́ mʋ bɛɛ, “Osunápʋ́, nwɛ́n nfɩ Yudafɔ ahandɛ bakle abʋda fʋ́ abwi mɔ. Mʋ́ fɛɛ fɛ́trá yinkí yɔ́ ɩnʋ?”
Támɛ amʋ́tɔ́ akʋ bɛblɩ́ bɛɛ, “Megyí oyin ánfɩ lóbwií ansibi obwiepʋ́ ámʋ ansíbi nɩ. Ntogyi sʋ́ ɔmɛtalɩ́ kɩ́tá Lasaro yáɩ́, alawú?”
Yudafɔ tsɔtsɔɔtsɔ bonu ánɩ́ Yesu laba Betania. Mʋ́ sʋ begya ɔkpa yɔ́ mʋ ɔkɩ́kpa. Megyí mʋ nkʋlɛ sʋ bɔyɔ́ ɩnʋ. Bɛyɛ́kɩ Lasaro amʋ́ʋ́ Yesu lɔ́kʋsʋ́a tsu afúlitɔ ámʋ ɛ́.
Brɛ́á Yesu lɛ́bláa amʋ́ asʋn anfɩ tá á, ɔlɛnatɩ́ yéŋaín.
Simon Petro lɛ́bláa mʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mɩ́ Wíé, megyí mɩ́ ayabi nkʋlɛ. Wuna fwɩ mɩ́ ɩbɩ pʋ́ mɩ́ nwuntɔ ɛ́.”
Yesu lɛ́fɩtɛ́ mʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Fówu mɩ́ sʋ? Ɔnɔkwalɩ ndɛ fʋ́ bláa. Fɔ́swɩɩ́ pʋ́ ɩbɩ wá ogyá tse sa fɛɛ fʋmeyín mɩ́ asa batɛ ɔbɛ́lɛ ɔnɔ́.”
Mmɛ́ɛtrá tɔɩ́ yɔ́ nkpá, tsúfɛ́ ɔyɩ́sʋ́ ogyípʋ́ ámʋ ɔbá. Ɔma túmi mɩ́sʋ́.
“Nabláa mlɩ asʋ́n anfɩ fɛ́ɛ́, mɛ́nɩ mlɩmɛ́ɛdɩda hógyitɔ.
Séi mʋ́ anɩlabɩ́ ánɩ́ fʋyin tógyítɔ́. Mʋ́ sʋ mehián ánɩ́ ɔhaa ɔbɛ́trá fɩtɛ́ fʋ́ asʋansʋ. Ɩ́nɩ lahá anɩlahogyi ánɩ́ lɛ́lɛ́ fotsú Bulu wá.”
Yesu lɔ́bɔ mpáɩ ánfɩ tá á, mʋa mʋ akasɩ́pʋ́ amʋ bɛnatɩ́ yɔ́tsʋn Kidron tsonkolitɔ wíé ndobíi kʋtɔ.
Bulu igyí ɔhapʋ́ dɛhɛn amʋ osúmpʋ́ ɔkʋ, ogyi ɔhá ámʋ́ʋ́ Petro lɛ́kpa mʋ ɩsʋ kʋlɛ amʋ mʋ pio lɛ́fɩtɛ́ Petro ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Megyí fʋ́a mʋnyɔ nowun ndobíi amʋtɔ nɩ́?”
Yesu lɛ́lɛ mʋ́ ɔnɔ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Nɩ́ megyí Bulu lɛ́ha fʋ́ ɔkpa á, tɛkɩ fʋma túmi kʋkʋ mɩ́sʋ́. Ɩ́nɩ sʋ ɔhá ámʋ́ʋ́ ɔlɔpʋ mɩ́ wá fʋ́ ɩbɩtɔ ámʋ lakpan dʋn fʋ́ klɛ́.”
Támɛ ɩsá akɔpʋ́ ámʋtɔ ɔkʋlɛ lɔ́pʋ mʋ pɩ́a wɔ Yesu abɩntɔ, ntsu mʋ́a obugya lɛfɛn dalɩ.
Kwasieda ámʋ ntʋ́pwɛsʋ á, akasɩ́pʋ́ amʋ befia. Befin obu wá ɩwɩ, tsúfɛ́ bʋdɛ Yudafɔ ahandɛ amʋ ifú nya. Ɩnʋ á, Yesu lɛ́bɛlɩɩ́ amʋ́ nsɩnɛ́, ɔlɛbláa amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ɩwɩ ilwíi mlɩ.”
Brɛ́á begyi nyankɩ atogyihɛ amʋ tá á, Yesu lɛ́fɩtɛ́ Simon Petro ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Yohane mʋ bi Simon, fʋtɔdwɛ́ mɩ́ dʋn fʋ́ aba ánfɩ lóó?”
Bowie wúlutɔ á, bɔdʋ yɔ́ abansʋ́rʋtɔ, ɔtɩ́nɛ́ ámʋ́ʋ́ bʋtsie yaɩ́ ámʋ. Sumbí ayɔpʋ́á bɔyɔ ɩnʋ gyí: Petro, Yohane, Yakobo mʋa Andrea, Filipo mʋa Toma, Bartolomeo mʋa Mateo, Alfeo mʋ bi Yakobo, Simon ánɩ́ ogyi ɩwɩsʋtsiá adunkápʋ́ ɔpasuatɔ ɔha pʋ́ oyin ɔkʋá bʋtɛtɩ́ mʋ Yakobo mʋ bi Yuda.
Ɩnʋ Petro mʋa mʋ aba dúɔkʋn ámʋ bɔkʋsʋ́ lɩ́ɩ́. Mʋ́ʋ́ Petro lótsu ɔmɛ fʋ́á bláa ɔdɔm amʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Apíó aba Yudafɔ pʋ́ mlɩ fɛ́ɛ́á mlɩbʋ Yerusalem, mlɩhɩɛ yaa asʋ, anlɛ asʋ́ntɔ́ suna mlɩ.
Fʋ́lósuná mɩ́ ɔkpa ánɩ́ ntsʋ́ʋn mʋ́sʋ́, mɩ́ anya nkpa ánɩ́ ɩtamatá.
Támɛ Petro lɛ́bláa mʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mma sika futútú ntɛ́ɛ pɛ́pɛ, támɛ nɛ́ha fʋ́ tɔ́á mbʋ. Kʋsʋ lɩɩ, afʋnatɩ Yesu Kristo Nasaretyin amʋ dátɔ́!”
Mʋ́mʋ́ tsú ndɛ mlɩa Israelfɔ fɛ́ɛ́ mlɩbɩ ánɩ́ Yesu Kristo, Nasaretyin amʋ túmi pʋ́ mʋ dátɔ́ oyin ánfɩ ɔ́lɩɩ́ mlɩ ansɩ́tɔ́ ánfɩ lanyá ɩlɔtsá. Mʋgyí ɔhá ámʋ́ʋ́ mlɩlɛ́da mántá oyikpalíhɛsʋ mɔ́ mʋ asa Bulu lɔ́kʋsʋ́a mʋ tsú afúlitɔ ámʋ nɩ.
Amʋ́tɔ́ ɔkʋkʋ mégyi ohian, tsúfɛ́ amʋ́á bʋbʋ ɔsʋlʋ́ʋ pʋ́ wóyí betsiá fɛ́ mʋ́, pʋ́ mʋ́ ɔnɔ́ kɔ́ba ba
Mʋ́ sʋ Bulu ɔtswɛ́kpa agyópʋ ɔhandɛ amʋ mʋa mʋ aba bɔyɔ yɛ́kpa sumbí ayɔpʋ́ ámʋ ba. Bɛkpa amʋ́ díín pʋ́ amʋ́ ba, tsúfɛ́ benya ifú ánɩ́ nɩ́ bɔpʋ́ ɩbɩ da amʋ́ á, ahá bɛ́da amʋ́ abwi.
Bɛlahá akʋ bɔwa afunu dɩ́nká mʋsʋ bɛɛ, “Oyin ánfɩ tɔtɔ́ɩ́ wɔ Bulu ɔtswɛ́kpa wankɩ́hɛ́ pʋ́ Mose mbla ámʋ ekekegyíɛkɛ.
Mose lénya nú asʋ́n ánfɩ alɩ, ɔlɛsrɩ́ dalɩ Egyipte ɔmátɔ́ yɔ́ Midiafɔ ɔsʋlʋ́sʋ. Oletsiá ɩnʋ kwɩ́ɩ́ abi anyɔ.
Stefano lɔ́mɔ mʋ asʋ́n ɔnɔ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Asʋtɔ-ɔnlɩn awíé, klʋntɔ bʋ mlɩ odwin. Mlɩlakíná Bulu asʋ́n ámʋ nu. Mlɩ ɛ́ mlɩtɔkʋ́sʋ́ lɩ́ɩ́ Ɔŋɛ Wankɩ́hɛ́ amʋ asʋ́nsʋ́ brégyíbrɛ́, fɛ́ alɩá mlɩ anáin amʋ betsiá bwɛ́.
Támɛ Petro lɛ́bláa mʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Fʋ́a fʋ́ kɔ́ba ámʋ nyɔ fɛ́ɛ́ mlɩhɩ. Tsúfɛ́ fʋkɩ fɛɛ, fɛ́talɩ́ pʋ́ kɔ́ba hɔ Bulu itokiehɛ́ ánfɩ.
Saulo aba ánɩ́ mʋa amʋ́nyɔ bʋna besi lɩ́ɩ́ díín. Bonu ɔmɛ amʋ, támɛ bʋmowun ɔhaa.
Ahá ánɩ́ bʋtsie Lida wúlutɔ pʋ́ Saron nsáɩntɔ fɛ́ɛ́ bowun oyin ámʋ. Mʋ́ sʋ bohogyi, bobuo anɩ Wíe.
Ɩnʋ Petro lɛ́kplɩ́ yɔ́tʋ amʋ́, bláa amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mɩ́gyí ɔhá ámʋ́ʋ́ mlɩdédunká ámʋ nɩ. Ntogyi sʋ́ mlɩná?”
Mʋ́ sʋ brɛ́á Petro lɔ́yɔ Yerusalem wúlutɔ á, mʋa ahógyipʋ akʋá bʋtekleá ahá bʋtɩ́ɩn keté asa abʋwie ɔpasua ámʋtɔ bɛbɩtɩ́ asʋ́n. Bɛfɩtɛ́ mʋ bɛɛ,
Herode lówun ánɩ́ ɩbʋ Yudafɔ ámʋ ɔdwɛ. Mʋ́ sʋ omesi, ɔlɛyɛ́kɩtá Petro ɛ́. Alɩ brɛ́ ámʋtɔ bʋdɛ Israelfɔ Bodobodo Mátúhɛ́Nkɛ gyí.
Mʋ nyawie gyí ɩnʋ ɔmásʋ́ ogyípʋ́ Sergio Paulo. Ɔmásʋ́ ogyípʋ́ anfɩ lɛ́tɩn ansɩ́. Ɔlɔwa bɛyɛ́tɩ Barnaba mʋa Saulo ba mʋ wóyítɔ́. Tsúfɛ́ odekléá mónu Bulu asʋ́n.
Ndɛ nabwɛ́ fʋ́ Sɩ́.’
Ifú mɛkɩtá Paulo mʋa Barnaba. Betsiá ɩnʋ wá ɔpá blɩ́ anɩ Wíe Yesu asʋ́n ámʋ wankláán. Yesu ɛ́ lɛ́lɩɩ́ amʋ́ ɔma, sʋ bɔbwɛ ofúla pʋ́ osúna pʋ́súná ánɩ́ mʋ awɩtɔlɛ asʋ́n ámʋ́ʋ́ bʋdɛblɩ́ ámʋ igyi ɔnɔkwalɩ.
Támɛ ahógyipʋ amʋ akʋá botsú Farisifɔtɔ bɔkʋsʋ́ lɩ́ɩ́ blɩ́ bɛɛ, “Ilehián ánɩ́ ɔmá bámbásʋ́fɔ ámʋ bɛ́tɩn keté, gyi Mose mbla ɛ́sʋ́.”
Ɔŋɛ Wankɩ́hɛ́ lalɛ́ súná anɩ, anɩ ɛ́ anɩlahɔ mʋ́ ánɩ́ ɩma alɛá abɔ́pʋ atɔ dwindwín kʋkʋ sʋ́rá mlɩ, dʋn mbla ánfɩ mʋ́ ɩwɩ dehián anfɩ.
Otsibi anfɩ lɛ́kplá buo anɩa Paulonyɔ. Ɔna ɔdɛkplʋ́n blɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Ahá ánfɩ gyí Ɔsʋ́sʋ́ʋ́sʋ́ Bulu ámʋ asúmpʋ́ nɩ. Amʋ́dɛ́ mlɩ nkpahɔ́ɔ ɔkpa suná nɩ́.”
Támɛ bʋmowun Paulo mʋa Silas. Mʋ́ sʋ bɛbɩtɩ́a Yason mʋa ahógyipʋ amʋ akʋ ya wúlu ahandɛ ansɩ́tɔ́, bʋdɛ okitikíti bɛɛ, “Ahá ánfɩ ná bʋdɛ agywɩɩn háan ɔyɩ́tɔ́ fɛ́ɛ́ nɩ́. Bawíé nfɩ,
Ɩ́nɩ ɔma a, Paulo lɔ́kʋsʋ́ tsú Atene yɔ́ Korinto wúlutɔ.
Bɛlɛ mʋ́ ɔnɔ́ bɛɛ, “Anɩmɔ́kʋ́nú kɩ ánɩ́ Ɔŋɛ Wankɩ́hɛ́ kʋ bʋ ɩnʋ.”
Ɔmá ámʋtɔ ahandɛ akpɔnkpɔntɩ akʋá bʋgyi Paulo anyawíe ɛ́ bɔwa obí lóyóbwií ɩpa há mʋ bɛɛ, ɔmáyɔ ofíakpa ɩnʋ.
Mlɩyin ánɩ́ mmɔpʋ asʋ́n ánɩ́ ɩbɛ́kpa mlɩ ŋáín mlɩ brɛ́á nɛda Bulu asʋ́n ámʋ ɔkan dɩnsʋ pʋ́ mlɩ wóyítɔ́.
Brɛ́á anɩlónu asʋ́n ánfɩ á, anɩa ahá ámʋ́ʋ́ bʋbʋ ɩnʋ ámʋ fɛ́ɛ́ anɩlókokóli Paulo anɩaa ɔmáyɔ Yerusalem.
“Mɩ́ asɩ́, apíó aba, mlɩyaa asʋ mɩ́ anlɛ mɩ́ ɔnɔ́ amlɩnu.”
Ɩnʋnʋ ahá ámʋ́ʋ́ bɛɛ abʋfɩtɛ Paulo asʋ́n ámʋ fɛ́ɛ́ badásáɩ́n. Ifú lɛkɩtá ɔhandɛ amʋ onutó ó, brɛ́á ɔlɛbɩ ánɩ́ Romayin Paulo gyí asa alahá bawá mʋ ɩkan.
Ɩnʋ nowun ánɩ́ amʋ́ mbla ɩwɩ nwɛ́ɛn bʋdegyí. Mʋ́ sʋ ɔmɔkʋ́bwɛ́ lakpan kʋkʋá bɔ́mɔ mʋ, ntɛ́ɛ bɔ́wa mʋ obu.
Ɔlɛbláa ɩsá akɔpʋ́ ɔhandɛ ámʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, ogyóo Paulo ɩwɩ wankláán, ɔha mʋ otsia iwilwiitɔ. Ɔhá mʋ aba ɔkpa abʋkɩ mʋsʋ.
Támɛ mmowun tsitsa kʋkʋ mʋ ɩwɩ ánɩ́ nɔ́wanlɩ́n mántá mʋsʋ bɔ́pʋ mʋ ya. Mʋ́ sʋ́ nakpá mʋ ba mlɩ ansɩ́tɔ́ nɩ́, títriu fʋ́ Owíe Agripa. Ndekléá atɛ́tɛ asʋ́n ámʋtɔ, ɔtɩ́nɛ́á ileyéyi a, mɩ́ anya asʋankʋ wanlɩ́n sɩ́sɩ́ mʋ.
Paulo lɛ́bláa mʋ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Brɛ́ tinbí o, brɛ́ tsɔtsɔɔtsɔ o, mɩ́ mpáɩ ánɩ́ ndɛbɔ há Bulu gyí, fʋ́a ahá ánfɩ mlɩdɛ́ mɩ́ asʋn blɩ́hɛ́ nu ndɛ ánfɩ fɛ́ɛ́ mlɛ́ba bɔbwɛ fɛ́ mɩ́. Támɛ bʋmáwa mlɩ ɩkan anfɩ mʋ́.”
Ɛkɛ dúanasɩ onyé á, afú ámʋ bʋ mʋ́sʋ́ ɩdɛ anɩda yáa nsɩnɛ́ ɩnʋ ɔpʋá bʋ́tɛtɩ́ mʋ́ Adriasʋ. Mʋ́ ɔyɩ́nsɩnɛ́ á, ntsusʋ-yibi ámʋtɔ agyʋ́má ayɔpʋ́ bosusúu ánɩ́ anɩlatá ɔsʋlʋ́ʋ tʋ tá.
Tsú ɩnʋ á, anɩlóbomlí tsʋn bowie wúlu yílé kʋá bʋtɛtɩ́ mʋ́ Regiosʋ. Mʋ́ ɔyɩ kɛhɛ a, afú kʋ lɔ́wa tsʋ́ʋn bɩ tsu ayasɩ fʋ́n. Nkenyɔ́ ɔma a, anɩlóyowie otsubúnɔ kʋá bʋtɛtɩ́ mʋ́ Puteoli.
Ɩna mʋsʋ Bulu lawá awɩtɔlɛ lɛ́ mɩ́ mʋ sumbí ɔyɔpʋ́, mɛ́nɩ nɛ́kpa ɔmá bámbásʋ́fɔ bɔ́hɔ mʋ gyi, nú mʋ ɔmɛ.
Mʋ́ sʋ nɩ́ fʋ́dɛ ahá ɩlá lɛ lakpan ánɩ́ fʋ́ onutó fʋ́dɛbwɛ sʋ á, bɩ ánɩ́ Bulu ɛ́ ɔbɛ́ha fʋ́ ɩpɔ́n. Fʋmɛ́ɛtalɩ́ kɔlɩ dalɩ mʋ ɩbɩ. Ntɛ́ɛ fʋmeyín alɩ?
Ɛkɛkɛɛkɛ! Megyí alɩ ígyi! Nɩ́ afunupʋ ahá fɛ́ɛ́ bʋgyi óó á, Bulu mʋ́ á, ɔnɔkwalɩpʋ ogyi. Igyi fɛ́ alɩá Owíe Dawid lɛ́bláa Bulu ɔbɛ́ɛ,
Ɔkpa ámʋ gyí ɔkpa ánɩ́ Bulu tɔtsʋn há ɔha asʋ mʋ ansɩ́tɔ́ nɩ́. Yesu Kristo hógyisʋ Bulu tɔtsʋn hɔ ɔhagyíɔha. Ma fʋgyi o, ma fʋmegyí o, nkʋ́nʋ fotsú o, nkʋ́nʋ fʋmotsú o, ɔhaa mɔ́tsʋn ɔtsan Bulu ansɩ́tɔ́.
Tsúfɛ́ ɔhɩ́ɛ́ oyin ánɩ́ Bulu ɔbɛ́talɩ́ bwɛ́ ɩtɔ́ ámʋ́ʋ́ alahɩ́ɛ́ há mʋ amʋ.
bopulá anɩ, tsúfɛ́ anɩa mʋnyɔ anɩlabwɛ́ kʋlɛ. Mʋ́ sʋ alɩ ámʋ́ʋ́ anɩ Sɩ́ Onumnyampʋ amʋ lɔ́kʋsʋ́a mʋ tsú afúlitɔ ámʋ a, alɩ kɛ́n anɩ ɛ́ abétsiá itsiá pɔpwɛtɔ nɩ́.
Tsúfɛ́ lakpan lénya ɔkpa tsʋn mbla ámʋsʋ mlɛ́ mɩ́, mɔ́ mɩ́.
Megyí Ɔŋɛ́ ánɩ́ ɩbɛ́ha mlɔ́bwɛ nkpábi, tsíá nyá ifú Bulu lɔ́pʋwá mlɩtɔ. Mboún Ɔŋɛ́ ámʋ lɔ́bwɛ mlɩ Bulu abí. Ɔŋɛ́ ámʋ sʋ anɩtɛtálɩ́ su kpolí Bulu anɩaa, “Abba, mɩ́ Sɩ́!”
Mɩ́ pɩ Israelfɔ gyí ahá ánɩ́ Bulu lɛ́lɛ pʋ́bwɛ́ mʋ abí. Amʋ́ ɔlɛlɛ mʋ numnyam súná. Ɔlɛka ntam há amʋ́, pʋ́ mʋ mbla wá amʋ́ ɩbɩtɔ. Olosuná amʋ́ ɔkpa ánɩ́ bɔ́pʋtswɛ mʋ. Ɔlɛbláa amʋ́ tɔ́á alahɩ́ɛ́ ánɩ́ ɔbɔ́pʋhá amʋ́ fɛ́ɛ́.
Támɛ Israelfɔ ámʋ́ʋ́ amʋ́ ansɩ́ lɛpɛ, bʋdɛ mbla ámʋsʋ gyí, Bulu ɔha amʋ́ asʋ ámʋ bʋmɛtalɩ́.
Brɛ́ bámbátɔ́ a, Yesaia lɔ́wa klʋn bláa amʋ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Bulu ɔbɛ́ɛ,
Mlɩ ahá ámʋ́ʋ́ mlɩmégyí Yudafɔ ámʋ mʋ́ á, oyí laláhɛ bámbi mlɩgyí, bɔpʋ mlɩ tsá oyí ámʋsʋ. Tɛkɩ ɩma ɩnʋ alɩ. Israelfɔ mʋ́ á, oyi wankláán ámʋ onutó abámbi bʋgyi, bɛkpalɩ́ amʋ́ tsítsá. Mʋ́ sʋ amʋ́ yinkía yi mʋ́ yintisʋ mɔ́ɔwa ɔnlɩn há Bulu.
Mlɩbʋa mlɩ aba Bulu ahá ánɩ́ bʋbʋ ɩkplántɔ. Mlɩyɩrɩ ɩwɩ hɔ afɔɔ́.
Nɩ́ anɩtsie nkpa á, anɩtsie ha anɩ Wíe. Awú ɛ́ á, anɩlawú há mʋ. Mʋ́ sʋ nɩ́ anɩlawú o, anɩtsie nkpa o, anɩ Wíe bʋ́ anɩ.
