Nɩ́ ɩwɩ ntobí ámʋ igyi toku kʋlɛ a, nkálɩ nyankpʋsa-oyí ámʋ ɩbɔ́bwɛ?
Ɔhá ánɩ́ ɔdɛ ɔblɩ́ɩ bambá blɩ́ nkʋlɛ tényá ɔwʋnlɩ́n Bulusúmtɔ́. Támɛ ɔhá ánɩ́ ɔdɛ Bulu ɔnɔ́ asʋ́n blɩ́ mʋ́ tɔwá ɔpasua ámʋ ɔwʋnlɩ́n.
