Ndɛ Bulu kokóli mbɛ́ɛ, ɔhá amlɩdwɛ aba dʋn alɩ, amlɩtɩn ansɩ́, nú asʋ́n ámʋ ɛ́ asɩ wankláán,
bwɛ́ mʋ ɩwɩ osúmpʋ́.
Ɩtráhɛ a, mɩ́ apíó, anɩ Wíe sʋ mlɩnya ansigyí. Ɩmɔkʋ́kpɔn mɩ ánɩ́ nɛ́trá wanlɩ́n asʋn kua kʋlɛ anfɩ sɩ́sɩ́ mlɩ. Igyi asʋ́n ánɩ́ ɩbɛ́kpa mlɩ ɛ́.
Mmɛdɛ́ asʋ́n ánfɩ blɩ́ pʋ́súná ánɩ́ mbʋ ɩkplántɔ, tsúfɛ́ nakásɩ́, nabɩ́ alɩá tɔ́á mbʋ ɩbɔ́fʋn mɩ, nɩ́ mbʋ óó, mma óó!
Mʋgyí nwun há mʋ nyankpʋsa-oyí, igyi ɔpasua ámʋ, ɔdɛ mʋ́ nkpa ha. Mʋlégyankpá kʋsʋ́ tsú afúlitɔ, ogyi tógyítɔ́ nkpá ogyápʋ.
Ɔhá ánfɩ odu lamáɩ́n ɩwɩ lɛ́ Kristo amʋ́ʋ́ ógyi ɔpasua ámʋ nwun ámʋsʋ. Tsúfɛ́ ɔpasua ámʋtɔ anɩ fɛ́ɛ́ anɩlɛ́tsa abasʋ, Kristo amʋ́ʋ́ ogyi nwun ámʋ dɛ́ anɩ ɔwʋnlɩ́n wa, mɛ́nɩ abɛ́dan alɩá Bulu déklé.
Nkpábi awíe, mlɩpʋ tɔ́á ɩbʋ alɛ́, igyi ɔnɔkwalɩ kpa mlɩ nkpábi, tsúfɛ́ mlɩ ɛ́ mlɩbʋ Owíe ɔsʋ́sʋ́.
Apíó, mlɩ onutó mlɩyin ánɩ́ anɩ mlɩ wá bá mɔbwɛ kpaalɩ.
Anɩ Sɩ́ Bulu onutó mʋa anɩ Wíe Yesu bʋfínki ɔkpa ha anɩ aba mlɩ wá.
Kristo lówu há anɩ, mɛ́nɩ mʋ bábɩ a, nɩ́ anɩlawú o, anɩbʋ nkpa o, anɩa mʋnyɔ abétsiá.
Nɩ́ mlɛtálɩ́ bwɛ́ ɩ́nɩ á, mlɩ sʋ ahá bɔ́pʋ numnyam há anɩ Wíe Yesu, mʋ ɛ́ ɔbɔ́wa mlɩ numnyam; fɛ́ alɩ ámʋ́ʋ́ anɩ Sɩ́ Bulu mʋa anɩ Wíe Yesu Kristo awɩtɔlɛ gyí ámʋ.
Támɛ mlɩmálu mʋ, mboún mlɩtɔɩ kpla mʋ fɛ́ mlɩ píó.
Ɔnɔkwalɩ ndɛ mlɩ bláa, mmɛdɛ́ afunu wa. Ɩ́nɩ sʋ́ Bulu lɛ́lɛ mɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, mbwɛ́ɛ mʋ asʋ́n ɔkan ɔdapʋ́, mʋ sumbí ɔyɔpʋ́ pʋ́ osunápʋ́ ha ahá ánɩ́ bʋmegyi Yudafɔ, mɩ́ ambla amʋ́ ɔnɔkwalɩ asʋ́n tsú Yesusʋ hógyi ɩwɩ nɩ́.
Bulu lótsu mʋ ya ɔsʋ́sʋ́ numnyamtɔ.
Ɩ́nɩ sʋ ndekléá asʋrapʋ amʋ́ʋ́ bʋmɔkʋ́dan amʋ bʋwúna tsia akúlu kwɩɩ abí, abʋkɩ amʋ́ wóyísʋ́, mɛ́nɩ bʋmɛ́ɛha anɩ alupʋ́  ɔkpa abʋblɩ anɩ ɩwɩ asʋn laláhɛ kʋkʋ.
Bla amʋ́ fɛɛ, bʋpʋ́ʋ amʋ́ kɔ́ba bwɛ yilé, amʋ́ yilébwɛ imoni. Bʋsánkɩ ɩbɩtɔ abʋkie atɔ́.
Kaɩn Yesu Kristo, Owíe Dawid mʋ na ámʋsʋ. Mʋ Bulu lɔ́kʋsʋ́a tsu afúlitɔ. Mʋ́gyí asʋn wankláán ámʋ́ʋ́ ndɛblɩ́ ámʋ nɩ.
Bɔ́bwɛ ɩwɩ fɛ́ Bulu bʋdesúm, támɛ békiná mʋ túmi. Lɛ ɩwɩ lɛ ahá ánfɩ odutɔ.
Anɩ Wíe ɔbɛ́lɛ mɩ́ tsú lalahɛ kugyíkʋtɔ. Ɔbɛ́kpa mɩ́ pʋtɔɔ alɩɩ yówie mʋ ɔsʋ́sʋ́ iwíegyí ámʋtɔ. Numnyam ɩbwɛ́ɛ mʋ klɛ brɛ́ fɛ́ɛ́tɔ́. Amen.
Suna ɔnɔkwalɩ amʋ, mɛ́nɩ ɔhaa mɛ́ɛtalɩ́ kʋsʋ́ lɩ́ɩ́ fʋ́ atosunáhɛ́sʋ. Fówun pɛ́lɩ bɛ́kɩtá fʋ́ alupʋ́, nɩ́ bʋmenya ɔlala blɩ́ tsú anɩ ɩwɩ.
Mɩ́ píó, ɔdwɛá fʋ́bʋ lahá ansɩ́ dɛ mɩ́ onutó óó gyí, ɩlawá mɩ́ atɛtɔ-ɔnlɩn. Tsúfɛ́ fʋ́ awɩtɔlɛ lahá Bulu ahá klʋn ladɩ́ amʋ́ asɩ.
Tɔ́á ɔlɛblɩ́ tsú mʋ abɔpʋ amʋ mʋ́ ɩwɩ gyí,
Brɛ́ itinbí kʋtɔ pɛ́ fɛba mʋ asɩ dʋn fʋ́ abɔpʋ.
‘Bʋtɛdálɩ mɩ́ ɔma brégyíbrɛ́,
Mʋ́ sʋ mlɩha abɔ mbɔ́dɩ́ awie ɔkpʋ́nʋ́ ɔdakpá ɩnʋ, mɛ́nɩ anɩtɔ ɔkʋkʋ méesin ɔkpatɔ fɛ́ alɩ ámʋ́ʋ́ Israelfɔ ámʋ bɔwa asʋtɔ-ɔnlɩn, besin ɔkpatɔ ámʋ.
Anyánkpʋ́sa akʋ bʋgyi fɛ́ ɔsʋlʋ́á itonu ntsuá nyankpʋ détswíe wʋlɩ́ mʋ́sʋ́, atɔ́ tɔwá alɛ́, wá labi há ahá ámʋ sʋ ámʋ́ʋ́ bɔdɔ mʋ́ ámʋ. Bulu toyúlá alɩ ahá ánfɩ odu.
Tsúfɛ́ bɔwanlɩ́n wá Bulu asʋ́n ámʋtɔ bɛɛ, “Bulu igyí ɔhapʋ́ fʋ́gyi brɛ́ fɛ́ɛ́tɔ́, fɛ́ Melkisedek.”
ɛkɛ ámʋ nɩ. Mɩ́ mlɩ Wíe dɛ́blɩ́.
Ɩ́nɩ sʋ́ bɔpʋ obugya sí Bulu ntam gyankpapʋ amʋ ɛ́sʋ́ asa ɩlɔyɔ agyʋ́má nɩ́.
Ɔŋɛ Wankɩ́hɛ́ ɛ́ légyi mʋ́ ɩwɩ adánsɩɛ súná anɩ. Olegyankpá blɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ,
Támɛ nɩ́ amʋ́tɔ́ ɔkʋ mɔ́wa klʋn kɩ́tá ɩwɩ mʋ hógyitɔ, oleyinkí ɔma mʋ́ á,
Hógyi lɛ́ha mʋ ɔlɛha Israelfɔ befi Katsʋn Nkɛ gyí asɩ. Ɔlɛha amʋ́ bɔpʋ obugya kpá amʋ́ obu-ɔnɔ́, mɛ́nɩ Bulu-ɔbɔpʋá ɔtɔmɔ́ ahá ɔmɔ́ɔpʋ ɩbɩ da amʋ́ bitɩ́.
Mlɩkɩ ánɩ́ mlɩtɔ ɔkʋkʋʋkʋ mɔ́ɔhʋlɩ́ɩ Bulu awɩtɔlɛ amʋ. Mlɩtɔ ɔkʋkʋ ɛ́ mási asʋ́n wá mʋ klʋntɔ, mɛ́nɩ ɔmɔ́ɔpʋ asʋ́n wá mlɩ nsɩnɛ́, iyinta mlɩtɔ akʋ.
Mʋ́ sʋ mlɩha adalɩ yɔ mʋ wá mmuátse ɩnʋ, abʋkpɔɩ anɩa mʋnyɔ.
Tsúfɛ́ ɔblɔ́ tamabwɛ́ tɔ́á Bulu tekle.
Alɩ́ ɩlɛba ha obu-ɔnɔ́ otsiápʋ́ Rahab ɛ́ nɩ́. Bulu lótsu mʋ ánɩ́ mʋ asʋ́n da ɔkpa, tsú tɔ́á ɔlɔbwɛ sʋ. Ɔlɔpʋ Yudafɔ akʋá bɛba bʋdɛ ansɩ́ wa kɩ mʋ ɔmátɔ́ ŋáín, ɔlɛha amʋ́ bɛtsɛ ɔkpa srɩ́.
Mlɩkpʋkpɛ manta Bulu, Bulu ɛ́ ɔbɛ́kpʋkpɛ́ manta mlɩ. Lakpan abwɛpʋ́, mlɩfwɩ ɩbɩ lɛ lakpanbwɛtɔ. Ahá ánɩ́ mlɩ agywɩɩn igyi anyɔ, mlɩha mlɩ klʋntɔ ɩtɩn.
Ndɛ mʋ́ wanlɩ́n sɩ́sɩ́ mlɩ ahá ánɩ́ Bulu lalɛ́ bwɛ́ mʋ abí, mlɩladásáɩ́n yɔ́bwɛ afɔɔ́ Ponto, Galatia, Kapadokia, Asia yɛ́dalɩ Bitinia ɔmátɔ́ fɛ́ɛ́.
Mʋ́ sʋ mlɩkpʋkpɛ ba anɩ Wíe Yesu Kristo wá. Mʋgyí nkpa Owíe nɩ. Kristo gyí fɛ́ ibwiá ahá bekiná mʋ́ ánɩ́ ɩma labi, támɛ Bulu lɛ́lɛ mʋ́ ánɩ́ ɩbʋ labi mʋ ansɩ́tɔ́.
Atsɩ, mlɩbu mlɩ akúlu alɩ kɛ́n, mɛ́nɩ nɩ́ amʋ́tɔ́ akʋ bʋmɔhɔ Bulu asʋ́nsʋ́ gyi kʋ́ráá, bowun mlɩ tsiátɔ́ a, ɩbɛ́tsɛ amʋ́, megyí mlɩ obétepí trá bláa amʋ́ asʋansʋ.
Ɩ́nɩ sʋ ɔmátrá ha ɔwɔ́lɩ laláhɛ igyi mʋsʋ. Mboún ɔhá Bulu apɛ́bwɛ itsia mʋ klʋntɔ mʋ nkpa ánɩ́ ɩlasí ɔyɩ́ ánfɩtɔ fɛ́ɛ́.
Mʋbʋ́ iwíegyí brɛ́ fɛ́ɛ́tɔ́. Amen!
Mlɩyin ánɩ́ Bulu mékiná atɩtɩfɔ ámʋ́ʋ́ bʋmobu mʋ amʋ ɩsʋbɩtɩ́. Mboún ɔlɛha ntsu lɛ́mɛ amʋ́ fɛ́ɛ́. Noa mʋa ahá abasíénɔ́ pɛ́ lésián. Noa lɛ́da ɔkan bláa ahá alɩ brɛ́ ámʋtɔ ɔbɛ́ɛ, bʋtsía tsiátɔ́á ilegyi Bulu ansɩ́.
Támɛ Bulu lɛ́hɩɛ ánɩ́ ɔbɔ́bwɛ ɔsʋ́ mʋ́a asɩ pɔpwɛ há anɩ. Ɔtɩ́nɛ́á ahá ánɩ́ amʋ́ asʋ́n da ɔkpa bétsiá. Mʋ́ anɩgyó nɩ́.
Ɔyɩ́tɔ́ atɔ́ ámʋ ɩkʋ gyí, atɔ laláhɛá ɩtɛdɩ́nká ɔha ɔwɔ́lɩ; atɔ́á ɔha towun, ɩtɛdɩ́nká mʋ ɔwɔ́lɩ pʋ́ ntobíá ɔha tɔpʋ́tsú ɩwɩ. Ɩ́nɩ ánfɩ odu kʋkʋʋkʋ imotsú anɩ Sɩ́ Bulu wá, ɔyɩ́ ánfɩtɔ itsú.
Nɩ́ ɔkʋ bʋ atɔ́, alawun ánɩ́ kʋ dɛ mʋ ba hián, támɛ omowun mʋ nwɛ há mʋ a, mʋ́mʋ́ ɔmɛ́ɛtalɩ́ blɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, mʋtɔdwɛ́ Bulu.
Ɔhagyíɔha ánɩ́ olohogyi ɔbɛ́ɛ, Yesu gyí Kristo, (ɔhá ánɩ́ Bulu ladá mʋ ofúli amʋ) a, Bulu mʋ Bi ógyi. Nɩ́ fʋtɔdwɛ́ ɔkwɩɩ́pʋ́ a, fɔ́dwɛ mʋ bi ɛ́.
Nɩ́ ɔkʋ ɔbá mlɩ wá, ɔmɛdɛ́ Kristo atosunáhɛ́ anfɩ suná á, mlɩmáhɔ mʋ wá mlɩ wóyítɔ́, mlɩmátsulá mʋ itsiá.
Alɩ ahá ámʋ bʋgyɔ́wɩ! Tsúfɛ́ bapʋ́ Kain amʋ́ʋ́ ɔlɔmɔ mʋ gyama ámʋ ɔkpa. Bakʋla sika yɔ́bwɛ tɔ́á Bileam lɔ́bwɛ, bakʋ́sʋ́ lɩ́ɩ́ Bulusʋ fɛ́ Kora.  Mʋ́ sʋ Bulu ɔbɛ́hɩ amʋ́.
Mʋ ayabi dɛ ogyá kpa fɛ́ kɔɔ́brɩ ánɩ́ bafwɩ́ mʋ́ lɛ́ ogyátɔ́ ɩnʋnʋ. Mʋ ɔmɛ idetsulá fɛ́ ntsuá ɩdɛkpa yi.
Támɛ asʋ́n ánɩ́ mbʋ ha fʋ́ gyí, fahá ɔtsɩ ámʋ́ʋ́ bʋtɛtɩ́ mʋ Yesebel, ɔdɛ mʋ ɩwɩ tɩ ɔbɛ́ɛ, Bulu ɔnɔ́sʋ́ ɔtɔɩ́pʋ́ amʋ dɛ́pʋ mʋ atosunáhɛ́ mlɛ́ mɩ́ asúmpʋ́, bʋdɛ atsɩ mʋ́a ayin asʋ́n wa, bʋdɛ ɔkpɩtɔ-atɔ́ ɛ́ gyí.
Ahá ánɩ́ ntɔdwɛ́ á, amʋ́ ntɔwá ɩyɩn wa, bɩ́tɩ́ amʋ́ ɩsʋ. Mʋ́ sʋ wa nsi, afʋdamli klʋntɔ.
“Fʋ́lɔ́fʋn ánɩ́ fótsu ɔwʋlʋ́ ámʋ,
Nwʋlʋ́táa lokuntá fɛ́ ɔwʋlʋ́, tsú mʋ́ nátɩ́. Abʋ mʋ́a ɔpʋ nsɩnɛ́ ɔsʋlʋ́ʋ fɛ́ɛ́ lɛdalɩ mʋ́ otsiákpá.
Ɔbɔpʋ náásɩ́ lɔ́fʋlɩ́ mʋ klɛ. Ɩlɔwɔ owí mʋ́a ɔtsra pʋ́ ntsrakpabitɔ yée asatɔ iku kʋlɛ. Mʋ́ fɛ́ɛ́ lodun. Ɩ́nɩ sʋ ɔyɩ kɛhɛ mʋ́a owi tahɛ́tɔ́ yée asatɔ iku kʋlɛ ɛ́ loklun.
Ɩnʋ ɔmɛ amʋ́ʋ́ ɩdɛ mɩ́ asʋ́n bláa tsú ɔsʋ́sʋ́ ámʋ lɛ́trá bláa mɩ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Yɔhɔ ɔwʋlʋ́ ámʋ́ʋ́ ɩlafínkí ámʋ lɛ Bulu-ɔbɔpʋ amʋ́ʋ́ ɔlɩɩ́ ɔpʋ mʋ́a ɔsʋlʋ́sʋ ámʋ ɩbɩtɔ.”
Brɛ́ lafʋn ánɩ́ fɛ́hɩ ahá ánɩ́ bamɔ́ ahá ɔyɩ́tɔ́ fɛ́ɛ́.”
Ɩnʋ bʋ́tɩ́ ámʋ lɛ́fɛn ntsu tsʋnhɛ dálɩ mʋ ɔnɔ́tɔ́ wʋ́lɩ́ ɔtsɩ ámʋ ɔma, mɛ́nɩ ɩbɛ́kɩtá mʋ nátɩ́.
Bulu-ɔbɔpʋ saasɩ ɛ́ búo amʋ́, ɔdɛblɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Nɩ́ ɔkʋ lósum ɔbwɩ ámʋ mʋa mʋ ɔkpɩ ámʋ, há bɔpʋ amʋ́ nsʋhɩ́ɛtɔ hɩɛ mʋ ɔsʋkpɩ ntɛ́ɛ mʋ ɩbɩ nsʋ a,
Ɔbɔpʋ nyɔɔsɩ lɛ́tsɛɩ́ mʋ klɛ wá ɔpʋtɔ. Ɔpʋ amʋ lémlí fɛ́ fúli obugya. Tógyítɔ́á ɔbʋ ɔpʋ amʋtɔ lówu.
Owíe okwesɩ gyí ɔbwɩ ámʋ́ʋ́ oletsiá, ɔtráa ɔma ɩnʋ séi ámʋ. Abasíénɔ́ ámʋtɔ ɔkʋlɛ ogyi. Mʋ ɛ́ ɔbɛ́hɩ fɛ́ mʋ aba ámʋ.
Mʋ ipian ámʋ́ʋ́ odewúun amʋ ɩbɔ́wa amʋ́ ifú. Mʋ́ sʋ bɛ́lɩɩ́ tsútsúútsú blɩ́ bɛɛ, “Gyɔwɩ nɩ́! Babilon gyɔwɩ nɩ́! Wúlu kpɔnkpɔɔnkpɔntɩ, nkálɩ sʋ Bulu labɩ́tɩ́ fʋ́ ɩsʋ ɔtsáwʋlɛ pɛ́ alɩ?”
Ɔsʋ́sʋ́ ɩsá akɔpʋ́ bʋdɩn mpɔnkɔ futútúsʋ́. Bɔwa ɔhráda atadɩɛá ɩlɔwankɩ́, ɩdɛ ogyá kpa bʋbuo mʋ.
Támɛ afúpʋ́á beyinkí mɩ́ ɔma, ahá ánɩ́ bʋmɔhɔ mɩ gyi, mbusuo abɔpʋ́, ahá amɔpʋ́, mbʋa atɔpʋ́, atɔ́ alapʋ́, ɩkpɩ atswɛ́pʋ pʋ́ afunupʋ fɛ́ɛ́ otsiákpá gyí ogyá paatɩ kpɔnkpɔntɩ, ogyá mʋ́a atonkodu ɩhɩ́ɛ́ detsií mʋ́tɔ́. Ɩ́nɩ gyí lowu nyɔɔsɩ amʋ nɩ.”
Mʋ́ʋ́ ɔlɛbláa mɩ́ ɔbɛ́ɛ, “Mápʋ atɔ lɛsúnáhɛ́ anfɩ ŋáín, tsúfɛ́ mʋ́ bábɩ lafʋn ta.
